N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 20 ยง 297.8 - Extensions of time

State Regulations

Administrative Code of the City of New York, ยง
11-1920

The provisions of Part 157 of this Title with respect to
extensions of time for New York State personal income tax purposes shall also
be applicable to extensions of time for City of New York earnings tax
purposes. Notes
